20170509 DML Synch two computers over ssh

To manually synchronize NVIDIA TK and Iggy.
SSH into the TK1
ssh ubuntu@192.168.2.201

And run this command:
sudo date --set="$(ssh user1@192.168.2.200 date)"

When prompted for passwords use the right ones for each machine:
TK1 User: ubuntu pw:ubuntu

